window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Larson has returned victorious from his battle with the pirates, but his quest to carve out his place in this new world is far from over. His respite from battle will be a short one as politics, creatures from the deep, pirates, and more will push him, the <i>Sea Venom</i>, and his crew to their limits.</p> <p>The forces arrayed against Larson are powerful, but he has a few tricks up his sleeve. A lifetime of naval service and a glimmer of knowledge from his old life on Earth will give him a powerful new weapon that just might turn the tide in his favor. With a loyal crew and a ship that is more than it seems, Larson stands ready to face all who stand in his way.</p>"; 
